{% comment %}

To add a header or a footer you can add the @page entry shown below to the <head> section of your html.
What shows up in the header/footer is specified in `content:`

{% endcomment %}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <style>
      @page {
        margin-bottom: 75px;
        @bottom-center {
          content: "Bottom Center";
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

{% comment %}
